channel.description: Alright.. how do i compile my server? i know what to click on (im pretty sure at lest) but when i click on 'compile' it says 'you do not have java (or jdk i cant remember..) 5.0 or 6.0 and i have jdk 6 update 10 (newest one..) and i also have the newest java.. so im just confused.. could sombody help please? thanks for reading and sorry if this is a retarded question for you..

item.description:
@gothaman wrote:

right click it and click edit the do ctrl+f an search for something like this

%programfiles%\JAVA\JDK1.6.0_05\BIN

then change it to this

%programfiles%\JAVA\JDK1.6.0_10\BIN

pm me if i dosent work
